# CBEC Solutions Landing Page - Environment Variables

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Formspree Configuration
# Sign up at https://formspree.io to get your form IDs
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Contact form submissions (required for contact page to work)
FORMSPREE_CONTACT_ID=your_contact_form_id_here

# Lead magnet download form submissions (optional)
FORMSPREE_LEAD_MAGNET_ID=your_lead_magnet_form_id_here

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Google Analytics (optional, for tracking)
# Create a GA4 property at https://analytics.google.com
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Format: G-XXXXXXXXXX
NEXT_PUBLIC_GA_MEASUREMENT_ID=

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Notes
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# - Variables prefixed with NEXT_PUBLIC_ are exposed to the browser
# - All other variables are server-side only
# - Never commit this file with real values to version control
# - Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your actual values
#
